\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Every new season in his life started with the decision to be obedient to something God was calling him to do. His life changed, the people around him have changed, he is sharing his faith more...everything changed in one moment..\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And today many of us in the room you'll get to have a moment.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We've been building up to our yeo and we do this every year to give God a moment in our lives to help us wrestle with our giving. \
